you pay them no mind

00:35:07.800 --> 00:35:08.510
and instead concern yourself

00:35:08.510 --> 00:35:09.760
with my master's private life?

00:35:09.760 --> 00:35:10.360
This isn't just

00:35:10.360 --> 00:35:11.320
your master's private life,

00:35:11.320 --> 00:35:12.120
Commander Yu.

00:35:12.550 --> 00:35:14.150
Why don't you think about it?

00:35:14.230 --> 00:35:15.510
Madam Bai's background is unknown,

00:35:15.510 --> 00:35:17.190
and now she's disappeared without reason.

00:35:17.190 --> 00:35:18.800
Is there truly nothing suspicious
about that?

00:35:18.800 --> 00:35:20.150
Could she be a pawn sent by Fengliu Shop

00:35:20.150 --> 00:35:21.590
to control Sword King Yu?

