00:40:11.360 --> 00:40:12.230
but, more importantly,

00:40:12.230 --> 00:40:13.710
his deceptive nature.

00:40:14.550 --> 00:40:16.710
He killed with one hand
while saving with the other,

00:40:16.710 --> 00:40:18.030
winning people's hearts

00:40:18.030 --> 00:40:19.560
while deceiving the world.

00:40:21.070 --> 00:40:22.550
Now look at Tang Lici.

00:40:23.480 --> 00:40:25.610
He uses the court's name as protection

00:40:25.840 --> 00:40:27.370
and commits heinous crimes

00:40:27.550 --> 00:40:29.280
under the pretense of justice.

00:40:29.710 --> 00:40:31.370
